channel.description: well im trying to find a decent size island that is white somewhere in my source, so i can start making kree and miniions on any idea what coordinates are for one?

item.title: Whats a coordinate for an icy island?
item.dc:creator: @Mighty_Penguin Mighty Penguin
item.description:
@Mighty_Penguin wrote:

Go to Fremminik Isles and go towards the castle place. Then noclip your way to the water, there should be a “icy” island around there.
